":1613661,"uid":324701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"你竟然可以忍到唔unfriend佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:22:09.000Z","msg":"Keep住傾計， 得閒在group度send啲facebook， video之類出嚟。 講自己冇立場， share下啫。<br />\n<br />\n佢又要費一大輪心機解釋狡辯， 都好大壓力㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a04349e0605278b9f19adfb06cf2614440aa0f9","tid":1613661,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f76a7a3d38160c456f0636ce8c0290c4f7d2b279","tid":1613661,"uid":153131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc70d6a2f2d676ba2e42d917310bea8bff545d0e","tid":1613661,"uid":272510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好 響學校附近播 有隻雀仔跌落水呀<br />\n尤其小學生最鍾意 唱改咗歌詞嘅歌，啲狗二代好慘㗎"},{"pid":"8a54ea17823091ad520d4ab978ab8a33d23f72d4","tid":1613661,"uid":329231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"每個人都做到"},{"pid":"fd59de86c311733fa98fb0915b641d041b7cb569","tid":1613661,"uid":266396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:16:40.000Z","msg":"已經被unfriend 晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777f54318c8afdbdc3aea4d090b3913dc0ef93a4","tid":1613661,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"人人都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}